    "v1": "Come, ye disconsolate, wher&#39;er ye languish; Come to the mercy seat, fervently kneel. Here bring your wounded hearts, here tell your anguish; Earth has no sorrow that Heav&#39;n cannot heal.",
    "v2": "Joy of the deso- late, light of the straying, Hope of the peni- tent, fadeless and pure, Here speaks the Comforter, tenderly saying, &quot;Earth has no sorrow that Heav&#39;n cannot cure.&quot;",
    "v3": "Here see the Bread of Life; see waters flowing Forth from the throne of God, pure from above; Come to the feast of love; come, ever knowing Earth has no sorrow but Heav&#39;n can remove."
  },
